  "detailed_description": "Take the Turn is a turn based multiplayer racing game for up to four players.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*** Features ***<br />\r\n- Play with people from all around the world or connect directly with your friends in private matches.<br />\r\n- Customize the look and stats of your racing car.<br />\r\n- Create your own tracks using the ingame editor and race other people on your own creations.<br />\r\n- Practice mode to improve your skills while offline.<br />\r\n- Crossplay between Mobile and PC",
  "about_the_game": "Take the Turn is a turn based multiplayer racing game for up to four players.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*** Features ***<br />\r\n- Play with people from all around the world or connect directly with your friends in private matches.<br />\r\n- Customize the look and stats of your racing car.<br />\r\n- Create your own tracks using the ingame editor and race other people on your own creations.<br />\r\n- Practice mode to improve your skills while offline.<br />\r\n- Crossplay between Mobile and PC",
